race.comment: LA PROFECIA (1) was well in the betting at the Gold Coast on debut but just ran into a couple better on that occasion. Will be better for that race day experience and where there's smoke there's fire. Rates the testing material. STEIN (6) hit the frame in town when at the races for the first time and should find this assignment a touch easier. Looms as the main danger. QUANTUM OVERDRIVE (2) is facing the starter for the first time but is sure to be well-educated out of the Archibald camp. Keep very safe. MISHANI VISION (5) has placed two of three overall, draws low and gets 3kg off with the claim. Plenty to like about her prospects. LITTLE MISS CLASSY (8) strips fitter second-up from the break and may trouble the judge with any luck from the wide draw.
